Name: fuel cell production, solid oxide, 125kW electrical, future | fuel cell, solid oxide, 125kW electrical, future | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/27:Manufacture of electrical equipment/279:Manufacture of other electrical equipment/2790:Manufacture of other electrical equipment
Description: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with unpressurised tubular stack design for central cogeneration use. Performance, stack lifetime and catalyst use according to expected future values for a serial product. Operation with connection to low pressure gas network. Electrical efficiency 47%, total efficiency 80%.
